I had to write it and if you really want you can read it but you must understand that it might be confusing and I am just a lil emotional at this time.......



Okay so here I am sitting in my room crying not even really sure why... I decided finally to stop thinking that i was gonna be able to go out with this guy I really liked... he is a friend of my friends and I met him at there house one night... he is really cool and there seem to be a lot of simialar intrest but I am not the chasing type i guess... especially since I don't see him in person and don't have a chance to talk to him  online since I doubt he even has any messengers... I have his number but i hate phones and it is hard to learn things about a person and have conversations through texts........ so i have been thinking about giving up on the idea on us going out or really doing anything because school is almost done and then I have to go home and it just seemed like a bad idea but I wasn't really thrilled at the idea of it all so I thought maybe I could have some hope and maybe something magical would happen but instead I have had two oppurtunities to hang out with him one was last night but i couldn't cause I had signed up to do this event til six in the morning... well then there was hope that he would hang out at my friends house tonight... will he showed but i took too long getting ready and talking to a few friends here and by the time that I was about to leave found out he had already left and that was it for me.... it has to be fate or something to lose out on the chance twice like this..... especially the one today... I really wont have a chance to see him again before I go home..... and even if I did there wouldn't be much of a point to it..... i would be about three hours away for three months.... I have given up on the thoughts of other crushes before but for some reason this when has got me into an emotional wreck.... which also has me questioning my sanity haha.... I dont know my head is going about a million miles an hour.... I am crushed more than i have ever been by a bf dumping me and I am just not understanding why..... oh well mike if it is meant to be it will happen when the time is right.... I should know better than to think that I really have much control in anything that happens to me.... but still I don't know right now i just hurt...... I should be over it in a couple days I just have to hope that it happens sooner then later.....  love you all ~Dee

OKay so I have a new crush and this guy is the top notch guy... best I have ever met so far.... He has all these qualities that I like and that should work out well with me... so i hope he likes me..... cause I am totally head over heels in lust with him

on another note I really really want to get the song john deere green.... I have had it stuck in my head since friday and I really really want it ok so that is all.... Love you all, ME

In all my disfunctional relationships this one has lasted me the longest... but I had to finally breakup with the boy cause I was sick of being in a relationship that was already over... why hang on to a title that really doesn't mean anything to us... we hadn't really talked or barely seen each other for almost a month... so about half of the time we were supposedly going out we weren't even talking to each other and so I got fed up and said this has to end and so it has..... I am a lil upset by it but it really was the best thing to do for all parties involved I believe.... it just seems so abrupt but that is okay... I just hope I can get over the fact that he has now ruined 'just to see you smile' for me which is a song that I really have enjoyed for many years and now it has been tainted.... I hate how relationships can do that to a person... especially me haha will I am in pretty good spirits right now and hope that this will mean I can have more fun.... haha we will see I guess.... will I should go take a shower now I will ttyl always with love, ME

sometimes I wish I could fly away to never-never land with peter pan but in those times I would be incapable of getting off the ground.  For those are the times that I am not thinking happy thoughts.  When I am happy why would I need to go anywhere else???

My keys were found so I am super excited cause I get my money back for replacing them and won't lose money on my chem drawer key so I am super excited about that... I am in a weird mood and I hope that it passes quickly cause it just makes me upset.... doesnt' help that I tend to listen to songs that are sad or moody but hey they are good songs... such as James Blunt song which I have stuck in my head... and Melissa Etheridge songs which just get me all on edge.... I dont' know hopefully I will be able to be happy with things soon cause I am a happy person and not being happy is just killing me.... oh and Doom which I watched really disappointed me I thought it would be better.... well I have things to do tonight so I hope I am in a better mood next time I write... Love always, ME

I had a blast in cumberland with my friend and her family... Her family is histerical and they are just sooo much fun... I reicieved a new nickname.... haha like I really needed another one haha but I think that it is kinda cool... I was invited to the weddin that is on my bday so I have a couple months to think about whether or not I want to go to that... I am not sure what I am gonna do... It should be an awesome time with drinking and tons of fun so I think I just might go... so I am not gonna go into everything that happened so yah I miss good times and that was a great time well I should go think some and get some sleep ttyl... love, ME

just cause I am here and I am bored... so I am going to my friends house for the night on saturday and I am super excited for this because I have yet to even go to her town and me and her always hangout so this will be a good opurtunity to meet more of her family and friends  then I already have thus far.... I have been working my ass off for my art class which is a lil ironic cause I only took that class so I could have enough credits to be a full term student... I am still having some issues about my ex... I dont' know why I can't let it go... I don't want to be with him and I we have both moved on to other people but yet it bugs me... with the way he treated me he doesn't deserve this emotional junk to be used on him but for some reason I can't help it.... I think me and my bf are going to make it to the one month aniversery this is a goal I have not yet obtained except with my ex's (meaning aniversery of our break ups haha I only count the one from my ex that is still my friend and a person that I cherish.... but we will talk about him some other time) but me and the boy seem to be going strong...  I should get going I will talk when I have something that makes more sense love always ME

yah I got to go out and have some fun for a change... I hung out with some of my coolest friends haha love yah guys... my boy went to and so that was cool.. we danced it up at the club even though the music wasn't too good till the last about hour or so.... met a new guy and he is fricken awesome too.... then I went with my friends to the hotel and drank for the first time in like a month or two and it was well awaited and deserved haha I had a blast and I am just happy to have friends like them... love always me

I don't know if there have been any changes on this thing since last time I was on it but it looks like there must have cause this page looks completely new to me hmmmmm maybe I will load a pic of me up on here cause I don't think I have done that yet.... so this is just one of many of these blog like things I have... I also Have myspace and facebook and a few others so this is kinda interesting to come back to the first one I had had... the one that started it all... haha ttyl ME

I have no idea what to do.   Why am I so consumed with guys??  Things would be so much easier if I wasn't but yet I am.  It is so hard cause almost every guy I want I can't have or I don't really try o get!?  Why do I torture myself??  I should prolly focus on my classes but that isn't working to well.  I hate whining but yet I am anyway...  I am having fun why do I consume myself with thinking I need a relationship, all it would do is get in the way!!  I have awesome friends and I am meeting all kinds of new people...  I can't believe how many new people I have met just with in this last year... I have met people who I do not know how I could have gotten on with out them before bu yet I want something more but at least I am not alone a lot of my friends seem to be in the same boat.  Especially G who is having a had time finding a guy he is into that is gay.  I should just wait till I get this diet thing going then maybe I can get some to look at my (besides the creeps like the Perv.)  I dont know.  I can't believe those girls who throw away good guys..like my friend "Hick" his ex gf must have been crazy because he is an awesome guy.  He's attracive and sweet and a good dancer (swing, baby.)  He is such a god friend and he is so much fun to hang out with.  I will miss him when he is gone. oh I should just give up but that is not me....I say I give up but in my mind I never do.. in some recess of my brain I keep thinkin will there is a chance.  Than llama Chris tells me that I should go for this guy who has a gf (11 months!) cause he say a "spark" between us.  If I did that I would hate myself and I don't think I could trust the guy.  I mean really that is just a horible thing to do.  will no one reads this anyway so I will stop ranting and maybe try to get something important done.  Wow can't believe that I haven't wrote anything about stargate but I guess I'll have to do that some other time.  Always ME

Hello all sorry that has it been so long.  I have been pretending to be busy plus I had spring break.  I have one thing to say that is really on my mind at this point in time:  I saw one of my friends msn names which said It is better to have love and lost than to have never have loved at all.  I have just realized how much I hate this phrase considering I have never loved ( well with the exception of family which I believe is suppose to be excluded in this statement and is worse if I consider those who do not love their family like I love mine).  This makes me feel like scum because I am not part of this better category.  I have lost but before I could get attached to anyone (or more specifically any guy).  Cause when I analyze me and the gay guy I fell for I think there was mostly lust in that as well as all my guy crushes that I have had in the past and even presently.  Having never been in a real relationship I feel that this comment is trying to take down all the single people who never had a chance3 for love since in my case I am seen as the friend not the girlfriend.  This has got to be yet worse for my gay friend who has to find a guy he likes and then find out if the guy is gay or straight  (or even bi as a case may be).  Am I always going to be helpless I wonder?  
             Oh my hick friend want me to say something about him and I only call him a hick because that is what he asked me to refer to him as.  He is an awesome guy and a good dancer (swing dancer not something liike napolean Dynamite would do).  Anyway there now he'll be appreciative he got mentioned.  Too bad it is in this entry but who really gives a damn.  Oh speaking of dams  we have a picture drawn by mr ADD on our door of a beaver and it says watchout for mr. beaver.  It is funny and cute.
             What is with all the guys who like blondes by the way??  Two really hott guys are wasating their time falling for only blondes.  WHat is the point of that seriously??! So I am not blonde and I will not dye my hair blonde either.  I should go drown myself in a puddle now.  I am not sure weather or not it is still raining hmmmmmmmmmmmm whatever.

I got to see my nephew though since one of his great grandmas on his fathers side died.  I had meet her a few times and she was a spunky old lady.  My sisterseemed a little worried about the whole ordeal which seems warrented since they didn't get there luggage back yet and her jacket and the little ones jacket were in there.  I hope they get it all back soon.  I can not wait to go see them over spring break.  I have to work tomorrow but I do not feel that I am completely over whatever I have.  Oh well I guess that will just have to do.  I wish I could go to the club I miss seeing him.  I know that I don't really have a chance with him but there is something about him that I just can't stand not seeing him less than weekly I wish I could see him daily. He is like a mystery that I just have to figure out and if I don't he'll drive me insane forever.  Oh nothing sppectacular happened at the island that night I l lost the 10 bucks I gambled but my nephew was adorable.  I got him to say the island is calling then he asked me who was it caling.  I thought that was so cute and that was all in the car on the way to the buffet.  Well anyway we h ad been in the resturaunt for about half an hour at least and he trys to get my attention and when he does he tells me "look at all the other people the island has called" and he begings to point out all the places the people are in the resturant.  Oh I love that little boy so much.  I wish that he lived closer to me but oh well.  My sister said that if she had known sooner that I had so much time between semesters she would have had me go back with them and sent me back to school on a plane.  Oh well more time with my mum who I think needs me more than my sister does.

I am home for christmaas and I have a whole month off.  The only thing that sucks is that my search for guys will be delayed since I willl not be able to fall for a guy so far from where I will be staying.  I met a guy yesterday but he was gay which sucks but it wasn't like I was head over heals for him he just seemed cool.  He works with one of my friendas from here home home.  Soon I'll get to see my nephew older.  He is my favorite out of my niece and nephews though when the nephew younger is older I will probably be fond of him too.  My niece is the oldest of my sisters kids but she is only six years younger than me and shes seams more like a sister than a niece.  She is also going through those ackward annoying teen years so it is hard to get along with her.  Anyway I am really excited since I haven't seen my nephew since the begining of oct.  He refused to go into my dorm room.  It may have been because of my roommate.  She has her eyebrow pierced and he is young so it may have scared him.  I heard stories about him that make me laugh he is so smart and such a pain, but he is just so adorable.  They are also bringing there new dog which excites me because I have always wanted one...wait a sec....yay they are here so I'll write more later.  Maybe after dinner at the island.

I took this from my brother who took it from someone else:

"Is there a point to life when your passion no longer wants you? Where do you go when the world gets blurry with tears? What next when you wipe the tears away and everything is still a blur? When do you just admit that if you can't make yourself care about the things you want to care about that you'd be better off with an empty skull. Can mistakes be washed away with pain? Can love be shared outward if it cannot be granted inward? Can i live again after dying once? If all i cause is pain will i ever see happiness? Will words ever mean anything? Will the lump in my throat ever go away? Will my questions ever be answered?'

...
I used to think that no, because you don't know what you're missing so it can't be that painful. That it'd be worse to love someone and loose them. Now I think differently. I want to know what it is like to be in love. Broken hearts hurt, but hearts that have never experienced love also hurt. What is the purpose of a heart? Not in a medical way, when people think heart they think love, and my heart isn't working, I haven't found love. Its not like I expect to find my soulmate at age 18, but you know what I mean... I long to know what its like to have someone care about you, to want to kiss you and hug you and be with you always. I want to know what its like to want to do anything for someone, I want to know what its like to have that. It seems like so many people just go from boyfriend to boyfriend, girlfriend to girlfriend, or just guy to guy and girl to girl. How do they do that? What's their secret? How is it so easy for them? I rarely even have crushes on people, because in the past things have never worked out, so I tell myself from the begining hey don't! And I don't develop a crush on them, maybe that's why I don't like anyone anymore, I won't let myself. It not a good feeling to like someone then hear stories about who they like or who they kissed or have them ignore you. It makes me sit there and think what's wrong with me? What is it about me that makes no guys want to be with me? And as I always say you can't help like who you like. They don't like me that way and its never going to change but I just wonder when I am going to find someone I like and they like me back... when is it ever going to work out for me? It sounds like I'm just complaining and whining if you think that I don't care. I was just sitting here and thinking okay so I find it a little pathetic that I'm 18 and never had a true boyfriend (true meaning not a middle school one that pretty much meant hey we're friends that like eachother but did nothing about that.) I've never been on a date, I've never kissed anyone, I guess I just find it sad. And I know that maybe other people my age haven't experienced those things either, but being a hopeless romantic I can't ever forget it and its always on my mind, driving me insane. I just don't know anymore...
